@startuml
title SomeTrails Register
actor User
participant "SomeTrails"        as ST
participant "Register Form"     as RF
participant "Auth Server"       as AS
participant "User Database"     as DB
participant "Email Service"     as ES
participant "Subscription Service"  as SUB

User -> ST  : Navigate to SomeTrails
ST   -> RF  : Display register form
User -> RF  : Enter email, username, password
RF   -> AS  : Submit registration
AS   -> DB  : Check email uniqueness
DB   --> AS : Email available
AS   -> DB  : Create user record
DB   --> AS : User created
AS   -> ES  : Send verification email
ES   --> User : Deliver verification link
AS   --> RF : Registration success
RF   -> SUB : Offer subscription
SUB  --> User : Present tier options
User -> SUB : Select tier (or skip)
SUB  --> ST : Redirect to logged-in site

@enduml
